Risk Management Plan
Armour-Eckrich Meats LLC 

I.	Introduction
A Risk Management Program has been implemented at the Armour-Eckrich Meats LLC (AEM), Hastings facility, for the reduction of accidental releases of hazardous materials. This Program summarizes the management, administrative, procedural, and technological controls that work together to minimize the risk to site personnel, contractors, visitors, and the community and environment at large of hazardous chemical releases. The Risk Management Plan (RMP) is organized to correspond with specific U.S. Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) RMP, Program 3 of 40 CFR 68, definitions and requirements of Subpart G, including: 
