II.	Armour-Eckrich Meats Policies To Protect Health, Environment, and Safety
Risk management and safety are important concerns at Armour-Eckrich; this RMP formalizes and documents these activities. Armour-Eckrich is committed to conducting its operations in a safe and responsible manner and to reducing risks to human health and to the environment. It is Armour-Eckrich policy to comply with all applicable federal, state, and local rules and regulations.

